Thai Boxing For You - the best Muay Thai app in the App Store

I'm sure everyone knows the names of Bruce Lee, Jaen-Claude Van Damme, Jackie Chan, Jet Li. Who of you would like in childhood to be like them? Be as courageous, strong and agile. App "Thai boxing for you" will help realize your dream.

Are you a beginner? A professional athlete or coach? This app is for you! It will help you to really learn and hone the art of Muay Thai. Your coach will be one of the most famous all over the world expert in Muay Thai.

TRAIN WITH THE CHAMPION
Author Maxim Slipchenko – 3-time World Champion, 2-time European Champion, World Cup winner and multiple champion of international tournaments in Muay Thai. He has managed and prepared 5 Muay Thai World Champions.

CONVENIENT INTERFACE
Includes technique demonstration, super combinations, clinch techniques, the best timer and much more

BIGGEST MEDIA LIBRARY
Over the 350 photos, 250 videos, step-by-step striking description

This package includes:
- 33 types of strikes in Muay Thai with a description, photos and videos;
- 8 types of clinches with a description, photos and videos;
- 3 types of cling holds with a description, photos and videos;
- 8 types of clinch defense with a description, photos and videos;
- 19 types of strikes in clinches, with a description photos and videos;
- the best 15 types combos of Muay Thai from world champion with a description, photos and videos;
- 5 types knockout combos of Muay Thai from world champion with a description, photos and videos;
- description and videos exercises for bag training from world champion;
- description and videos exercises for pad training from world champion;
- the best hand wraps with a description, photos and videos;
- amazing boxing timer;
- super punch video.

THANK YOU goes to everyone who has downloaded Thai Boxing For You App!
